    "A final 100 Ma snapshot \u2014 zircons coloured red (near a trench, < 700 km) vs. blue (interior, \u2265 700 km). Most of the red dots cluster along the contemporaneous Andean-style margins, exactly as you'd expect from the Jian et al. classification."
